text: Siddharam Satlingappa Mhetre is a member of the 13th Maharashtra Legislative Assembly. He represents the Akkalkot Assembly Constituency. He belongs to the Indian National Congress,He is from Lingayat community ==References== Category:Members of the Maharashtra Legislative Assembly Category:Maharashtra MLAs 2014–2019 Category:People from Solapur district Category:Marathi politicians
